{"tid":2126542,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"基因研究證政策失誤引毒入城","createTime":"2020-07-27T01:55:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-27T01:55:05.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ffe30463a218e78fd1575604f17ca8192789e3ce","tid":2126542,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T01:55:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200727/YFMCARKFLAOF6KGV43XQ5DFPHE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200727%2FYFMCARKFLAOF6KGV43XQ5DFPHE%2F&d=EOe11knUQePtQJIakN8qxzC6QH3F2wvzJ1VFJz7MVw4%3D&h=43daf621\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200727%2FYFMCARKFLAOF6KGV43XQ5DFPHE%2F&h=a2199ff0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200727/YFMCARKFLAOF6KGV43XQ5DFPHE/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n基因研究證政策失誤引毒入城<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/kPvXYPYDvxIGSjM4kyWeMikR2gs=/640x807/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/YA6LDS2YS5WMQ24TIGOHQTZKDI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FkPvXYPYDvxIGSjM4kyWeMikR2gs%3D%2F640x807%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FYA6LDS2YS5WMQ24TIGOHQTZKDI.jpg&h=2c385775&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n蕭傑恒團隊研究發現，多名病人的病毒基因與哈薩克同源。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】多位政府專家顧問認為，第三波疫潮源自豁免檢疫人士。理大醫療科技及資訊學系副教授蕭傑恒團隊，隨機抽取這波疫情26個病人病毒樣本分析，發現均帶有主流的D614G基因變異，涵蓋哈薩克機組人員、彬記、港泰、莎莎員工以至屯門富臨大型群組，當中19份更完全一樣，結果符合袁國勇、許樹昌及梁卓偉三位專家推論。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n基因與哈薩克同源<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：林鄭硬頸累事 建制也不滿<br />\n<br />\n蕭傑恒指。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n蕭指樣本中第1326號病人、哈薩克返港的42歲男機組人員，是首位沒病徵人士，報住銅鑼灣一酒店，其樣本與禮頓山家庭群組四名患者完全一樣，但與上述19份樣本稍有分別，相信今次疫潮很可能是哈薩克、菲律賓主流的D614G基因突變病毒來港後，再轉變成相對穩定的基因排序，繼而極速散播社區。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。"}]}